ğŸ› ï¸ Step 1: Create a New Pipeline Job in Jenkins
1ï¸âƒ£ Go to Jenkins Dashboard â†’ New Item
2ï¸âƒ£ Enter Job Name (e.g., GitHub-Pipeline-Job)
3ï¸âƒ£ Select Pipeline â†’ Click OK
4ï¸âƒ£ Scroll down to Pipeline Definition
5ï¸âƒ£ Select Pipeline script from SCM
6ï¸âƒ£ Under SCM, select Git
